cs.DC, cs.CC, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.PL

This paper discusses benchmarking cloud services and their underlying systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). It also covers topics related to Cloud Computing (cs.CC) and Software Engineering (cs.SE) such as performance isolation and service level objectives. Additionally, it touches on aspects of Computer Security and Cryptography (cs.CR) and Programming Languages (cs.PL) in terms of operational risk and designing new metrics.
